- Yes.

264
00:22:10,822 --> 00:22:13,115
- I'll check and get back to you.
- Okay.

265
00:22:23,209 --> 00:22:25,920
It's an important audit
on one of our subsidiaries.

266
00:22:26,003 --> 00:22:27,129
Let me finish it.

267
00:22:27,213 --> 00:22:29,423
Put all the info on our cloud server.

268
00:22:29,507 --> 00:22:31,175
I'll take a look
and allocate someone else.

269
00:22:35,638 --> 00:22:38,599
NOH KI-JUN'S PROJECT TRANSFER

270
00:22:38,683 --> 00:22:41,143
NO FILES OR FOLDERS
NAMED NOH KI-JUN'S PROJECT TRANSFER

271
