288
00:24:14,654 --> 00:24:16,030
HAEMU PHARMACEUTICAL

289
00:24:20,076 --> 00:24:22,078
CONFIRMATION NEEDED,
HAEMU PHARMA BUSINESS REPORT

290
00:24:23,621 --> 00:24:24,956
BUSINESS REPORT

291
00:24:25,039 --> 00:24:26,499
HAEMU PHARMACEUTICAL INC.,
CEO JEON JAE-YEOL

292
00:24:31,504 --> 00:24:33,464
Put the garlic cloves sideways.

293
00:24:33,547 --> 00:24:35,383
This is whole fresh garlic.

294
00:24:35,675 --> 00:24:37,760
