- Add oil...

301
00:25:02,284 --> 00:25:05,955
- Wait. Sesame oil.
- One spoonful of garlic.

302
00:25:06,497 --> 00:25:08,499
Sesame oil. I don't have any oil.

303
00:25:09,333 --> 00:25:11,085
CANOLA OIL, GROUND GARLIC,
PERILLA SEED OIL, SESAME OIL

304
00:25:16,298 --> 00:25:17,425
All right.

305
00:26:05,264 --> 00:26:07,349
It tastes so good. My gosh.

306
00:26:19,236 --> 00:26:20,237
Mr. Noh?

307
00:26:21,697 --> 00:26:23,157
Did you come in this early?

308
00:26:24,617 --> 00:26:26,077
