can affect business matters.

316
00:27:07,701 --> 00:27:09,954
And they're harder to handle
because emotions are involved.

317
00:27:11,122 --> 00:27:12,164
I believed that

318
00:27:13,124 --> 00:27:16,627
with your confidence and intuition
that keep you from being swayed

319
00:27:17,753 --> 00:27:20,172
you'd be able to handle them well,
and I was right.

320
00:27:26,137 --> 00:27:27,304
Is that all?

321
00:27:28,264 --> 00:27:29,306
Is there really

322
00:27:31,433 --> 00:27:32,434
no other reason?

323
