334
00:28:12,683 --> 00:28:13,726
JEI MEDICAL FOUNDATION:
500 MILLION WON

335
00:28:14,935 --> 00:28:17,313
But the actual owner
of this entity is

336
00:28:21,358 --> 00:28:22,359
Vice President Jeon Jae-yeol.

337
00:28:23,736 --> 00:28:24,862
This foundation

338
00:28:26,113 --> 00:28:27,990
was founded by Mr. Jeon, right?

339
00:28:35,664 --> 00:28:36,874
Now tell me.

340
00:28:37,583 --> 00:28:38,834
Are they related?

341
00:28:39,543 --> 00:28:42,296
This case and
why you sent me to Team Three.

342
00:28:46,550 --> 00:28:49,303
Let's make a minor change
to your role, Mr. Noh.

343
00:28:54,183 --> 00:28:57,102
NOH KI-JUN, AUDIT TEAM 1 TURNOVER

344
00:28:57,186 --> 00:28:58,604
DELETE PERMANENTLY

345
00:29:01,398 --> 00:29:02,733
DO YOU WISH TO PERMANENTLY DELETE
ALL FOLDERS AND FILES?

346
00:29:02,816 --> 00:29:03,817
YES

347
00:29:03,901 --> 00:29:05,986
FOLDER WAS PERMANENTLY DELETED

348
00:29:08,822 --> 00:29:10,658
Yes, I halted the investigation.

349
00:29:13,619 --> 00:29:16,247
