unnecessarily.

357
00:29:33,722 --> 00:29:36,058
- It would've become political...
- And he would've gotten hurt.

358
00:29:36,850 --> 00:29:38,269
VP Jeon, I mean.

359
00:29:44,858 --> 00:29:47,528
Did he ask you to help him out?

360
00:29:49,029 --> 00:29:50,572
He doesn't know that I know.

361
00:29:59,623 --> 00:30:02,835
You're meticulous with a clear
distinction between work and life.

362
00:30:02,918 --> 00:30:05,087
Did you really sweep this
under the rug yourself

363
00:30:05,838 --> 00:30:08,299
for fear that our VP would get hurt?

364
00:30:12,177 --> 00:30:15,014
Even if I don't do anything,
this will come out.

365
00:30:15,514 --> 00:30:16,765
So do whatever it takes

366
00:30:17,683 --> 00:30:19,059
