that wasn't presented beforehand.

385
00:33:05,301 --> 00:33:08,262
Director Park Sang-hwan
has something he'd like to suggest.

386
00:33:08,637 --> 00:33:10,973
- Please speak.
- Yes.

387
00:33:11,682 --> 00:33:14,852
