by Vice President Jeon Jae-yeol.

392
00:33:31,327 --> 00:33:33,787
However, the president
is still standing strong.

393
00:33:33,871 --> 00:33:36,749
Also, his condition does not change

394
00:33:36,832 --> 00:33:41,128
