400
00:34:08,656 --> 00:34:09,990
Wasn't he with the vice president?

401
00:34:10,574 --> 00:34:12,159
He must've betrayed him.

402
00:34:14,328 --> 00:34:15,496
Silence, everyone.

403
00:34:17,289 --> 00:34:22,544
Now, let us vote on the agenda
which Director Park has proposed.

404
00:34:22,920 --> 00:34:24,588
Those who agree to appoint

405
00:34:24,672 --> 00:34:28,008
Managing Director Jeon Sang-yeol
as the co-vice president

406
00:34:28,092 --> 00:34:31,887
