please raise your hand.

407
00:35:22,438 --> 00:35:23,647
Hello, Director Park.

408
00:35:24,106 --> 00:35:26,025
- I owe it all to you. Thank you.
- Don't mention it.

409
00:35:26,483 --> 00:35:28,027
I should start lining up
on his side, too.

410
00:35:38,078 --> 00:35:40,331
- Congratulations, Mr. Jeon.
- Ms. Joo.

411
00:35:41,373 --> 00:35:45,586
The sudden agenda had me flustered,
so I forgot about you.

412
00:35:45,794 --> 00:35:47,755
Did you say you had
another item to report on?

413
00:35:48,255 --> 00:35:50,591
Would you like
to report it in writing?

414
00:35:51,508 --> 00:35:55,804
- No, there's nothing, sir.
- All right.

415
00:35:56,263 --> 00:35:58,557
- Mr. Managing Director.
- Now the vice president.

416
00:35:59,016 --> 00:36:00,476
Goodness.

417
00:36:00,559 --> 00:36:02,519
Please help me out.

418
00:36:02,603 --> 00:36:04,646
- Why don't we go out and eat?
- Sure.

419
00:36:04,980 --> 00:36:06,190
Congratulations.

420
00:36:06,648 --> 00:36:07,858
I owe it to you.

421
00:36:10,194 --> 00:36:12,279
I'll need your guidance.

422
00:36:12,363 --> 00:36:14,948
- Goodness, you don't need that.
- I do.

423
00:36:15,324 --> 00:36:16,492
THE RECENT BOARD MEETING WAS INSANE

424
00:36:16,575 --> 00:36:18,118
THE DIRECTORS UNDER THE VP
HAVE LINED UP UNDER DIRECTOR JEON

425
00:36:18,202 --> 00:36:21,580
No way. So do we need approval
from two vice presidents from now on?

426
00:36:21,663 --> 00:36:24,333
Goodness. How will things work out
in the office?

427
00:36:24,416 --> 00:36:26,126
Isn't it obvious?

428
00:36:27,002 --> 00:36:28,087
We should side with S.

429
00:36:29,213 --> 00:36:31,632
I heard this
from the executive assistants.

430
00:36:31,715 --> 00:36:34,551
Director Park used to be
on Vice President Jeon's side

431
00:36:34,635 --> 00:36:36,595
