during this meeting.

432
00:36:37,054 --> 00:36:38,680
- My gosh.
- Office politics are scary.

433
00:36:39,807 --> 00:36:41,392
Gosh, so this is how it turned out.

434
00:36:41,475 --> 00:36:43,018
- What now?
- Whose side are you on?

435
00:36:43,310 --> 00:36:44,728
- Me?
- Yes.

436
00:36:45,145 --> 00:36:47,648
- I'm on your side.
- Cut it out.

437
00:36:48,941 --> 00:36:49,983
What about you?

438
00:36:53,445 --> 00:36:55,906
The report on the director... No.

439
00:37:53,130 --> 00:37:55,799
MR. NOH KI-JUN

