441
00:38:21,617 --> 00:38:23,118
After the beep,
you will be charged...

442
00:38:23,202 --> 00:38:25,078
JOO IN-A

443
00:39:00,864 --> 00:39:05,619
SEARCH: JOO IN-A

444
00:40:05,971 --> 00:40:09,474
BOO SE-YOUNG, HEAD OF HR

445
00:40:11,768 --> 00:40:15,063
Hey, do you realize
what time it is right now?

446
00:40:15,147 --> 00:40:16,273
Se-young.

447
00:40:17,774 --> 00:40:19,192
