454
00:40:34,916 --> 00:40:37,044
There are hospitals in the US, too.
Don't worry.

455
00:40:37,127 --> 00:40:39,087
And the company will cover
all medical costs.

456
00:40:39,171 --> 00:40:40,297
Isn't that amazing?

457
00:40:41,214 --> 00:40:43,342
