477
00:42:09,344 --> 00:42:10,679
What's going on
with my appointment to the US?

478
00:42:12,431 --> 00:42:14,224
It was already confirmed
that you were going.

479
00:42:14,766 --> 00:42:16,351
It's a great opportunity for you

480
00:42:16,435 --> 00:42:18,562
and if you're going anyway,
it's better to go soon.

481
00:42:18,645 --> 00:42:20,981
In the California branch,
you'll get to experience

482
00:42:21,064 --> 00:42:22,774
