486
00:42:44,671 --> 00:42:46,840
I'm not some kind of wuss
who can't understand that.

487
00:42:47,716 --> 00:42:49,050
I honestly blamed myself

488
00:42:49,134 --> 00:42:51,052
thinking if I had cornered you
too harshly.

489
00:42:51,928 --> 00:42:54,931
"Sure, when someone
you barely knew back in school

490
00:42:55,015 --> 00:42:57,559
suddenly shows up with a favor,
even that's difficult to turn down.

491
00:42:57,642 --> 00:43:00,604
So she may want to cover up
her ex-boyfriend's mishap."

492
00:43:01,271 --> 00:43:04,357
I thought I overreacted and regretted
getting carried away by my emotions.

493
00:43:06,610 --> 00:43:07,819
You didn't overreact.

494
00:43:10,906 --> 00:43:12,324
I can't promise you

495
00:43:14,701 --> 00:43:16,161
