to Jeon Jae-yeol?

502
00:43:45,315 --> 00:43:47,150
- No, that's not the case.
- Then what?

503
00:43:48,568 --> 00:43:51,196
How am I supposed to understand
this whole situation?

504
00:43:51,613 --> 00:43:52,739
Do I

505
00:43:56,076 --> 00:43:57,494
